starting_post.message:
Other than the issues I posted earlier this is a great map IMO, good luck with ranking it!
P.S You do know that you need a full spread to rank a map right? https://osu.ppy.sh/wiki/en/Ranking_criteria#rules.1 read here, good luck again and have a great time mapping!

02:55:297 (3,4,5) - これ02:55:608 (6) - の同じようにしたとわかりますが
スタックしたほうがいいと思います
https://reiolily.s-ul.eu/7P0pga7y

02:54:675 (5,1,2) - の１/１gapから出て2回 カーソルを加速しないといけなくてプレイで違和感が出ちゃいます。
https://reiolily.s-ul.eu/FzMiBPG0

これは絶対だめだと言ってないんですがセクションの動きに比べてほぼ真っすぐスナップ的なジャンプな感じなので急にこんな動きが混ざると（曲そんなに変わってませんし）よくないだとお思います
You could try removing a bit mid sections to give players a bit of rest since the map is currently very dense.

00:43:045 (4) and 00:44:062 (4) are mapped on silence so you could remove them, 00:49:825 (2,3,4) this is timed incorrectly so try to time it to the actual vocals instead of the beat (since in this part the vocals are slightly earlier than the beat itself) or just remove it.
The offset should be adjusted slightly to 1,690 (+7)
